<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827; line-height: 1.3;">
  Welcome to Mellow Menu<% if @user.name.present? %>, <%= @user.name %><% end %>!
</h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
  Your account is all set up. Start building your first smart menu and let your guests order the way they want — straight from their phones.
</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 32px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6;">
  Head to your dashboard to get started.
</p>

<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <a href="<%= root_url %>"
         style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 36px; background-color: #2563EB; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.01em;">
        Go to Dashboard
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 32px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.6;">
  If you have any questions, reply to this email or <a href="https://www.mellow.menu/#contact" style="color: #2563EB; text-decoration: none;">contact us</a>.
</p>
